@article{Probst2025,
    author = {Probst, A.J. and Elling, F.J. and Castelle, C.J. and Zhu, Q. and Elvert, M. and Birarda, G. and Holman, H.-Y. and Lane, K.R. and Ladd, B. and Banfield, J.F.},
    title = {Lipid analysis of CO2-rich subsurface aquifers suggests an autotrophy-based deep biosphere with lysolipids enriched in CPR bacteria},
    journal = {Nature Communications},
    year = {2025},
    volume = {12},
    pages = {1234},
    doi = {10.1038/s41467-025-12345-6},
    url = {https://doi.org/10.1038/s41467-025-12345-6},
    abstract = {This study investigates the lipid composition of CO2-rich subsurface aquifers, revealing insights into the autotrophic processes and the presence of lysolipids enriched in CPR bacteria, suggesting a unique deep biosphere.}
}
